id: pm-vnie
title: "ADR: Three-tier metadata cache (light scalars / bodies / collections) keyed by file stat"
description: Three-tier metadata cache (light scalars / bodies / collections) keyed by file stat
type: Decision
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[5]: adr,architecture,"area:storage",cache,performance
created_at: "2026-05-31T19:47:00.495Z"
